<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The patch adds two new classes Lucene/Analysis/TokenFilter/ShortWords.php and Lucene/Analysis/TokenFilter/StopWords.php. The first class filters out short words (minimum length can be configured), the second one words from stop word list (it can be loaded from file or from an array).</p>

<p>The patch also adds support for "null tokens" to Lucene/Analysis/Analyzer/Common classes.</p>

